QuestData.Title: Strange Gears
QuestData.Description:
<Oddly, the seed within the automa's innards is still very much alive.
Are they all like this?>
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Winding Seeds from the automa in the Blooming Foundry.
QuestData.RewardText:
<Koh Shira examines the piece of the automa--entwined with living vines.>
This cannot be.
Automa do not have vines within them. But these automa do.
This... is beautiful.
